    <h2><b>Discover</b> a new way to listen to your music library.</h2>
    <p class="p_medium">    
        <b>MPfm</b> is a music player made specifically for musicians. It may look like any other music player, but
        if you are a musician, it offers interesting features 
        such as <b>time shifting</b>, <b>loops</b> and <b>markers</b> to 
        help you pick songs by ear. Click <a href="/features" title="MPfm Features Page">here</a> to know more about MPfm.
    </p>
